title: Boxhead Zombie Wars for itouch
description:
Hey guys this is the official app ov Boxhead made for itouch i bought on Itunes.
I must warn you before you download, I was a little disappointed because its so different from the pc version but yet again, its a itouch game right?

Well the same weapons are:
Pistol
Shotgun
minigun
Barricades
Barrels
C4 packs
and many more upgrades

Oh and theres only 3 rooms to play with.
This is not the Trial Version!!!!
I bought it with my own money and here i am to share.

Lucifer Crow :)
